text_block_list.name: Curren Chan
text_block_list.text:
Hey, hey, there's this super 
cute cake shop!

text_block_list.name: Curren Chan
text_block_list.text:
If Curren were to eat their cake, 
cute x cute would make for the ultimate 
cuteness collab, don't you think?♪

text_block_list.name: Curren Chan
text_block_list.text:
I wish you could see me at 
my cutest, onii-chan～…

text_block_list.name: Curren Chan
text_block_list.text:
I wish you could see me at 
my cutest, onee-chan～…

text_block_list.name: Curren Chan
text_block_list.text:
If you got me one, I think it would push 
the cuteness through the roof♪
